            'Yes вҖ” with the right model size. A laptop with 8 GB RAM running a 7B model at Q4_K_M quantization produces 10вҖ“25 tokens/sec on CPU and 50вҖ“80 tokens/sec on Apple Silicon. This is slow compared to cloud APIs, but fast enough for interactive use.',
            'The practical ceiling on most 8 GB laptops is a 7B model. A 13B model at Q4_K_M requires ~9 GB of RAM вҖ” technically possible on 16 GB machines but leaves little headroom for the OS and other applications.',
            'For [what are local LLMs](/local-llms/what-are-local-llms) and a full explanation of RAM requirements, see the dedicated guide.',
