            'Windows laptops with discrete NVIDIA GPUs can be faster if VRAM is sufficient (8 GB+). An NVIDIA RTX 4060 laptop GPU (8 GB VRAM) runs a 7B model at 60вҖ“90 tok/sec вҖ” comparable to Apple M3 Pro. The downside is higher battery drain and heat generation.',
