            'This is impractical for interactive chat but usable for batch processing вҖ” summarizing documents, generating reports, or processing files overnight. For interactive use, the minimum practical hardware is a machine that can achieve 8+ tok/sec, which requires either Apple Silicon or NVIDIA GPU offloading.',
