            '**Japan (METI)**: For Japanese enterprises, Qwen2.5 72B is the recommended 70B model вҖ” its native Japanese tokenization is 30вҖ“40% more efficient than Llama for Japanese text. On a Mac Studio M2 Ultra (64 GB): `ollama run qwen2.5:72b`. METI AI governance requires documenting hardware and model versions. The `ollama ps` output provides exact model identification for compliance records.',
            '**China**: Qwen2.5 72B (Alibaba) running locally satisfies data localization under China\'s Data Security Law (ж•°жҚ®е®үе…Ёжі•) while delivering 84% MMLU quality. Enterprise teams commonly deploy on dual-GPU servers (2Г— RTX 4090, 48 GB VRAM combined). For CAC compliance: a locally-hosted Qwen2.5 72B serving internal users is outside the CAC provider definition вҖ” it is not offered as a public service.',
