      intro: 'Running a 70B model (normally requires 40+ GB) on 24 GB VRAM is possible with aggressive quantization (Q2вҖ“Q3) and layer offloading, but the result is slow (~3вҖ“5 tokens/sec). As of April 2026, this is impractical for real-time chat but viable for batch processing or experimentation.',
