            '**Model quantization:** Q4 vs FP16 uses 4Г— less VRAM, same speed. Reduces GPU count needed.',
            '**Batch size:** Larger batches = lower cost per request (but higher latency).',
            '**Auto-scaling:** Scale down at night, scale up during day (saves 30вҖ“50% cloud costs).',
            '**Multi-tenancy:** Run 2вҖ“3 models per GPU (if VRAM allows). Higher utilization.',
