      seoTitle: 'VRAM Calculator: How Much GPU Memory for Local LLMs?',
      intro: '**For 7B models, you need 8GB VRAM; for 13BвҖ“22B, 12вҖ“16GB; for 70B, 24GB minimum.** As of April 2026, these numbers assume Q4 (4-bit) quantization. Full-precision (FP32) models need 2вҖ“3Г— more VRAM and are rarely practical on consumer GPUs. The formula is: Model size (billions) Г— 2 bytes (FP32) Г· quantization factor.',
