      seoTitle: 'llama.cpp vs Ollama vs vLLM: Speed, Features, Complexity Comparison',
      intro: '**llama.cpp is fastest per-token for small models; Ollama is simplest; vLLM is best for throughput/batching.** As of April 2026, choose based on use case: casual chat вҶ’ Ollama; single-user speed вҶ’ llama.cpp; multi-user/batching вҶ’ vLLM. All three run the same models and produce identical outputвҖ”speed/throughput differ.',
      metaDescription: 'llama.cpp vs Ollama vs vLLM: Speed benchmarks, feature comparison, batching, throughput. Which backend? April 2026. Free beta вҖ” April 2026.',
