            '**Ollama:** Easiest to use. One command, auto-download models. Trade-off: 5вҖ“10% slower throughput than llama.cpp.',
            '**vLLM:** Highest throughput (tokens/sec) on batched requests. Best for production API servers. Steeper learning curve.',
            'Single-user chat: llama.cpp or Ollama (nearly identical speed).',
            'Multi-user API: vLLM (3вҖ“5Г— higher throughput).',
            'Casual use: Ollama (simplicity wins).',
            'All three produce identical model outputsвҖ”speed/feature differences only.',
